articles.title: Russian Luna-25 sends first picture of Moon, shows region permanently hidden from Earth - India Today
articles.description: The far side of the moon, also known as the "dark side," is the hemisphere of the moon that is permanently hidden from Earth's view due to synchronous rotation.
articles.content:
Russia's Luna-25 spacecraft has sent back its first images of the moon from lunar orbit. The images feature the south polar crater Zeeman, located on the far side of the moon.
